OL,3,CNew Labour MS says UK Government
OL,4,Cissues played factor in historic
OL,5,CSenedd defeat
OL,7,FA newly elected Labour Member of the
OL,8,FSenedd has criticised the UK Labour
OL,9,FGovernment saying they have not
OL,10,F"delivered change at the pace they
OL,11,Fpromised", partly blaming them for the
OL,12,Fparty's election result in Wales.
OL,14,FLabour MS Huw Thomas, who was formerly
OL,15,Fthe Cardiff Council leader, told ITVs
OL,16,FSharp End, "There have been issues
OL,17,Fwith the UK Labour Government. Keir
OL,18,FStarmer himself has acknowledged that.
OL,26,@rD@AOUsD@IO]xD@LOU
OL,1,Wj5hw}j5 ~shws                   G1/9
OL,2,W+.-'*%/"-$+,(,'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BWales News CReg TV FThis Day
FL,465,460,260,120,000,100
PN,46402
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F464A1778785872
OL,3,CNew Labour MS says UK Government
OL,4,Cissues played factor in historic
OL,5,CSenedd defeat
OL,7,F"The perception of the UK government
OL,8,Fhas not delivered change at the pace
OL,9,Fthat they promised when they were
OL,10,Felected back in 2024. I think that was
OL,11,Fcertainly a factor on the doorstep."
OL,13,FMr Thomas, who was elected last week,
OL,14,Frefused to say whether he thought the
OL,15,Fembattled prime minister should
OL,16,Fresign. He said, "I want to
OL,17,Facknowledge that Keir Starmer has been
OL,18,Freally good to Wales.
OL,26,@oD@AOUsD@dO]xD@ROU
OL,1,Wj5hw}j5 ~shws                   G2/9
OL,2,W+.-'*%/"-$+,(,'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BWales News CReg TV FThis Day
FL,465,460,260,120,000,100
PN,46403
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F464A1778785872
OL,3,CNew Labour MS says UK Government
OL,4,Cissues played factor in historic
OL,5,CSenedd defeat
OL,7,F"I'm very much hoping that the UK
OL,8,Fgovernment continues to deliver to
OL,9,FWales, and that will be part of our
OL,10,Frole as Welsh Labour in the Senedd, to
OL,11,Fcontinue to make the case for that as
OL,12,Fwell."
OL,14,FHis comments come as pressure mounts
OL,15,Fon the prime minister to step down
OL,16,Fafter historic Labour losses in the
OL,17,Felections last week, including Labour
OL,18,Flosing control of the Senedd for the
OL,19,Ffirst time.
OL,26,@oD@AOUtD@FO]
OL,1,Wj5hw}j5 ~shws                   G3/9
