OL,3,CNew Labour MS says UK Government
OL,4,Cissues played factor in historic
OL,5,CSenedd defeat
OL,7,FAlmost 100 Labour MPs have called for
OL,8,Fthe prime minister to resign or to set
OL,9,Fout a timetable for his departure.
OL,11,FOne of those calling for him to resign
OL,12,Fis the MP for Pontyrpidd, Alex Davies-
OL,13,FJones, who resigned as Minister for
OL,14,FVictims and Tackling Violence Against
OL,15,FWomen and Girls.
OL,17,FShe urged the prime minster to step
OL,18,Fdown after the "catastrophic" election
OL,19,Fresults.
OL,1,Wj5hw}j5 ~shws                   G4/9
