OL,3,CNew Labour MS says UK Government
OL,4,Cissues played factor in historic
OL,5,CSenedd defeat
OL,7,FOn May 13 Labour's affiliated unions
OL,8,Fcalled for a plan to be put in place
OL,9,Ffor the election of a new leader of
OL,10,Fthe Labour Party.
OL,12,FA statement from the TULO group, which
OL,13,Frepresents 11 unions, said Labour
OL,14,F"cannot continue on its current path".
OL,16,FOther political parties had their say
OL,17,Fon Sharp End about the prime ministers
OL,18,Ffate.
OL,26,@vD@AOUvD@eO]
OL,1,Wj5hw}j5 ~shws                   G5/9
