OL,3,CNew Labour MS says UK Government
OL,4,Cissues played factor in historic
OL,5,CSenedd defeat
OL,7,FReform UK's Joe Martin said that
OL,8,FLabour "certainly can't turn their
OL,9,Ffortunes around in this election cycle
OL,10,Feither.
OL,12,F"Politics has changed in 2020. It's
OL,13,Fdifferent to how it was when Tony
OL,14,FBlair was elected, for example. The
OL,15,Fprimary issues that face the country
OL,16,Faren't economic. It's not class or
OL,17,Fnationalisation versus privatisation.
OL,18,FIt's about issues like identity.
OL,26,@pD@HOUtD@AOU
OL,1,Wj5hw}j5 ~shws                   G6/9
OL,2,W+.-'*%/"-$+,(,'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BWales News CReg TV FThis Day
