CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F464A1778785872
OL,3,CNew Labour MS says UK Government
OL,4,Cissues played factor in historic
OL,5,CSenedd defeat
OL,7,F"Multiculturalism versus heritage and
OL,8,Ftradition and the prioritisation of
OL,9,Fnational self-interest over the
OL,10,Fmaximisation of global welfare."
OL,12,FMair Rowlands from Plaid Cymru said,
OL,13,F"It's worth noting that the Prime
OL,14,FMinister didn't mention Wales once in
OL,15,Fhis speech (on Monday), not one word
OL,16,Fabout that historic Senedd result, and
OL,17,FI think it's clear this situation is
OL,18,Funsustainable for the Prime Minister.
OL,26,@oD@AOUrD@`O]uD@AOUwD@LpmwD@Vpn
OL,1,Wj5hw}j5 ~shws                   G7/9
OL,2,W+.-'*%/"-$+,(,'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
