OL,3,CNew Labour MS says UK Government
OL,4,Cissues played factor in historic
OL,5,CSenedd defeat
OL,7,FMs Rowlands said, "We hope for
OL,8,Fstability as soon as possible so that
OL,9,Four governments can work together
OL,10,Fconstructively."
OL,12,FReturning Conservative Senedd member,
OL,13,FSam Rowlands, told ITV, "It looks like
OL,14,Fthe end is nigh in terms of his (Keir
OL,15,FStarmer's) premiership.
OL,17,F"It's clearly a very difficult
OL,18,Fposition for him. I think anyone in
OL,19,Fthat position must be questioning all
OL,20,Fsorts of things, trying to hang on.
OL,26,@oD@SOUrD@PO]uD@YOUvD@apmwD@JpnyD@AOU
OL,1,Wj5hw}j5 ~shws                   G8/9
