OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F464A1778785872
OL,3,CNew Labour MS says UK Government
OL,4,Cissues played factor in historic
OL,5,CSenedd defeat
OL,7,F"To be fair, Keir Starmer was elected
OL,8,Fas the leader of the party, with the
OL,9,Flargest number of MPs in the House of
OL,10,FCommons, so he has a mandate of sorts.
OL,12,F"A significant number of MPs have
OL,13,Fclearly lost confidence in him, and
OL,14,Fthat's why we've called for him to go."
